## typeSerializers variable

A dictionary of serializers of particular types returned by a flux query. See [https://v2.docs.influxdata.com/v2.0/reference/syntax/annotated-csv/\#valid-data-types](https://v2.docs.influxdata.com/v2.0/reference/syntax/annotated-csv/#valid-data-types)

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
typeSerializers: Record<ColumnType, (val: string) => any>
```
